Description

The armored knights of the Military Order of Santiago are specialists in naval and deep space operations. This new Infinity unit box compiles all the different weapon options of these servo-powered warriors. Here you will find the previously released Spitfire and Combi Rifle versions as well as the new Boarding Shotgun and another Combi Rifle sculpt. The most extreme courage is displayed in the risky boarding actions of the Knights of Santiago!

Box contains:

1x Knight Of Santiago (AP CCW)

1x Knight Of Santiago (Boarding Shotgun)

1x Knight Of Santiago (Spitfire)

1x Knight Of Santiago (Combi Rifle)

Properties
